@startuml fig-project-presentation
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
title Structura Prezentare Proiect (7-10 min)

card "1. Introducere (1 min)\nNume proiect, tehnologii, echipa" as intro #E3F2FD
card "2. Demo Live (4 min)\nStart curat, configurare, functionalitati, captura" as demo #C8E6C9
card "3. Arhitectura (2 min)\nComponente, flux date, decizii design" as arch #FFF3E0
card "4. Intrebari si Aparare (3 min)\nIntrebari tehnice, lectii invatate" as qa #FCE4EC

intro -d-> demo
demo -d-> arch
arch -d-> qa

legend bottom
Lista verificare:
README complet
Demo testat pe VM curat
Video backup inregistrat
Fisiere PCAP pregatite
endlegend
@enduml
